<topic id="xslt-quick-assist">
  <title>XSLT Quick Assist Support</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>XSLT<indexterm>Quick Assist feature</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_pcb_cgk_54b">The <xref keyref="glossentry_quick-assist"><term>Quick Assist</term>
        support</xref> helps you to rapidly access search and refactoring actions. If one or more
      actions are available in the current context, they are accessible via a yellow bulb help
        (<image href="../img/QuickAssist16.png"/>) placed at the current line in the stripe on the
      left side of the editor. Also, you can invoke the <term>Quick Assist</term> menu by using the
        <uicontrol product="developer editor"><shortcut>Alt + 1</shortcut></uicontrol><uicontrol
        product="developerEclipse editorEclipse"><shortcut>Ctrl + 1</shortcut></uicontrol>
        (<uicontrol product="developer editor"><shortcut>Meta + Option +
        1</shortcut></uicontrol><uicontrol product="developerEclipse editorEclipse"><shortcut>Meta
          1</shortcut></uicontrol> on macOS) keyboard shortcuts.</p>
    <p id="p_qcb_cgk_54b">Two categories of actions are available in the <term>Quick Assist</term> menu:<ul
        id="ul_ckb_cfc_c4">
        <li id="li_rcb_cgk_54b" irina="irina">
          <p id="p_scb_cgk_54b">Actions available on a selection made inside an attribute that contains an XPath
            expression:</p>
          <p id="p_tcb_cgk_54b">
            <dl id="dl_ucb_cgk_54b">
              <dlentry id="dlentry_vcb_cgk_54b">
                <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/CreateTemplate16.png" id="image_wlq_4fn_wr"
                    />Extract template</uicontrol></dt>
                <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/extract_template_short_desc"/></dd>
              </dlentry>
              <dlentry id="dlentry_wcb_cgk_54b">
                <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/CreateStylesheet16.png" id="image_p2z_2fn_wr"
                    />Move to another stylesheet</uicontrol></dt>
                <dd><ph
                    conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/move_to_another_stylesheet_short_desc"
                  /></dd>
              </dlentry>
              <dlentry id="dlentry_xcb_cgk_54b">
                <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/XSLLocalVariable16.png"/>Extract local
                    variable</uicontrol></dt>
                <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/extract_local_var_sh_desc"/></dd>
              </dlentry>
              <dlentry id="dlentry_ycb_cgk_54b">
                <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/XSLVariable16.png"/>Extract global
                    variable</uicontrol></dt>
                <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/extract_global_var_sh_desc"/></dd>
              </dlentry>
              <dlentry id="dlentry_zcb_cgk_54b">
                <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/XSLLocalParam16.png"/>Extract template
                    parameter</uicontrol></dt>
                <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/extract_templ_param_sh_desc"/></dd>
              </dlentry>
              <dlentry id="dlentry_adb_cgk_54b">
                <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/XSLParam16.png"/>Extract global
                    parameter</uicontrol></dt>
                <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/extract_global_param_sh_desc"/></dd>
              </dlentry>
            </dl>
          </p>
          <p id="p_bdb_cgk_54b">
            <fig id="fig_pmp_k3c_c4" product="developer editor">
              <title>XSLT Quick Assist Support - Refactoring Actions</title>
              <image href="../img/xslt_quick_assist_refactoring_actions.png" id="image_jpc_43c_c4"/>
            </fig>
          </p>
          <p id="p_cdb_cgk_54b">
            <fig product="developerEclipse editorEclipse" id="fig_ddb_cgk_54b">
              <title>XSLT Quick Assist Support - Refactoring Actions</title>
              <image href="../img/ec_xslt_quick_assist_refactoring_actions.png"
                id="image_nqc_yjc_c4"/>
            </fig>
          </p>
        </li>
        <li id="li_edb_cgk_54b" irina="irina">
          <p id="p_fdb_cgk_54b">Actions available when the cursor is positioned over the name of a component:</p>
          <p id="p_gdb_cgk_54b">
            <dl conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/quick_assist_actions_list" id="dl_hdb_cgk_54b">
              <dlentry id="dlentry_idb_cgk_54b">
                <dt/>
                <dd/>
              </dlentry>
            </dl>
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul></p>
